      <title>毛伊岛野火发生后，贝索斯承诺提供 1 亿美元，但没人知道它的去向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/bezos-promised-100-million-after-maui-wildfire-but-no-one-knows-where-it-s-gone</link>
